juniFileTransferAgentV1.name: juniFileTransferAgentV1
juniFileTransferAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the File Transfer component of the JUNOSe
        SNMP agent.  This version of the File Transfer component was supported
        in JUNOSe 1.x system releases.

juniFileTransferAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the File System application in JUNOSe.
